{"tid":2028391,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"［集思廣益］除咗眾籌登報仲有冇嘢可以make noise?","createTime":"2020-05-21T19:23:46.000Z","updateTime":"2020-05-22T01:57:07.000Z","uid":131766,"like":1,"dislike":2,"uniUserReply":4,"replies":[{"pid":"577600510b5584a5ce9606321eac5427941cfd0b","tid":2028391,"uid":131766,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-05-21T19:23:46.000Z","msg":"{69前氣氛返哂黎}我地急需一個低風險門檻嘅全民表態行動<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/2027915\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/2027915</a><br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區<br />\n<br />\n<strong><span style=\"color: pink;\">白宮聯署買裝？<br />\n雖然一定唔會彩鳩你但如果一日內有幾十萬人簽可以引起關注令多啲人想知發生緊咩事？<br />\n始終人地國家嘅嘢唔夠爆冇人會想知<br />\n</span></strong><br />\n<span style=\"color: orange;\">抖陰玩具車challenge?<br />\n世界各地嘅人都畀抖陰洗晒腦<br />\n人就最偽善最鍾意企係道德高地扮大愛<br />\n可以開始醞釀下 令佢地覺得拍條片就好正義爭取緊自由咁<br />\n要講明拍條咁嘅片都會畀人封帳 等多啲人屎忽痕走去試</span><br />\n<img src=\"https://thumbs.gfycat.com/AnnualFarFirecrest-size_restricted.gif\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fthumbs.gfycat.com%2FAnnualFarFirecrest-size_restricted.gif&h=26e3741e&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"a59ddacc57450bc22a7939b9894ffeff5af292bd","tid":2028391,"uid":242358,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-05-21T19:24:45.000Z","msg":"終於唔玩膠啦咩衰仔<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/aura.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"7d692b1b72aa7e9834e943ff25c3b7d0a29831dd","tid":2028391,"uid":131766,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"a59ddacc57450bc22a7939b9894ffeff5af292bd","tid":2028391,"uid":242358,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-05-21T19:24:45.000Z","msg":"終於唔玩膠啦咩衰仔<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/aura.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-05-21T19:27:39.000Z","msg":"晴晴<img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"2bafda101ac508d579910640267a87c95fcc5be5","tid":2028391,"uid":242358,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"7d692b1b72aa7e9834e943ff25c3b7d0a29831dd","tid":2028391,"uid"